rd in 2012.Mr Andreas Lauenroth, Executive Director Technical, Volkswagen India Private Limited, commented, "'Think Blue. Factory.' is a holistic approach which motivates our employees to implement the 'Think Blue. Factory.' ideas not only in the plant but also in their personal lifestyle."One of the next steps towards achieving the targets of the "Think Blue. Factory." initiatives is the inauguration of a Biogas plant in the premises of the Volkswagen Pune factory. Monthly biological waste of approximately 10 tonne will be fed to the highly automated and modern Biogas plant which will recycle the waste to produce cooking gas. This ecologically produced gas will be supplied back to the central kitchen for cooking processes.
