des. That's orders of magnitude faster, and we're already seeing that some species are challenged by that rate of change," he said.\u000a\u000a... contd.\u000a\u000aALSO READ Islamists rally in Egypt ahead of referendum vote, 3 killed\u000a\u000aPlease read our terms of use before posting comments
