ject to an international assessment process that could test the commitments, individually and in the aggregate, for adequacy \u2014 against the goal of not allowing global temperatures to rise more than two degrees celsius \u2014 and equitable burden sharing.\u000a\u000a... contd.\u000a\u000aALSO READ The taper tigers\u000a\u000aPlease read our terms of use before posting comments
