te buildings, including apartments where solar energy could be adopted, for common lighting and water supply."A master plan will be prepared in consultation with the stake holder committee and solar city cell that have been formed by the SMC. Once the master plan will be ready by 2012, the civic body will submit a draf plan to the union ministry of new and renewable energy for the grant of solar city status," a senior officer said.
